description.narrative: This activity (Humanitarian Emergency Secondments Facility) is a component of Humanitarian Emergencies Secondment Facility reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £4,632,598. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Relief co-ordination and support services. , with the following implementing partners: CANADEM, Crown Agents Limited, Danish Refugee Council, Norwegian Refugee Council, RedR, United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA). The start date is 10-07-2013 and the end date is 31-12-2017.
